Xfce4 Xmas Desktop

YouTube Video: https://youtu.be/0nZENNP9HXU

Packages Need:

mplayer
handbrake (or other transcoder)
shantz-xwinwrap-bzr (AUR)
xscreensaver

Optional
compton-git
comptray
compton-conf

Christmas_Icons:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/0BxhBaqtjMTGZSjdDbnBsanBSc3c/edit
Xmas Movies:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B1gwPhZ-BsWEeDZqUFlXMlVzS00/view?usp=sharing
Scripts:
https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B1gwPhZ-BsWEcHU5MVFkOXptaVU/view?usp=sharing

Suggested Command Keys:

CTRL+ALT+~ = compton on
CTRL+ALT+z = compton off

CTRL+ALT+, = multiple animated movies
CTRL+ALT+m = single animated move
CTRL+SHIFT+Q = wallpaper rotation

CTRL+ALT+. = kill all animations
